## 🏛️ PHASE 3 & 4: IMPLEMENTATION EVIDENCE

### GAP §12 — Agent Orchestration (Phase 3)
> *Source: Phase 3 spec §Orchestration*

**Implementation:** [orchestrator.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/agent/orchestrator.py)
- **Finite Reasoning Loop:** Implemented using a strict [for](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/event_bus/store.py#149-172) loop over `max_reasoning_steps`.
- **Metering Integration:** `self._metering.record()` called after every AI response ([L116](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/agent/orchestrator.py#L116)).
- **Correlation ID:** Propagation verified across all tool-calls and task results ([L150](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/agent/orchestrator.py#L150)).

### GAP §13 — Agent Runtime & Managed Providers (Phase 4)
> *Source: Phase 4 spec §Runtime*

**Implementation:** [runtime.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/agent_runtime/runtime.py)
- **Agent Registration:** [register_agent()](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/interfaces.py#45-50) validates identity and enforces budget.
- **Identity Revocation:** [unregister()](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/agent_runtime/runtime.py#99-150) fully revokes identity via [IdentityService](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/identity/service.py#19-299) and emits `agent.unregistered` ([L116](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/agent_runtime/runtime.py#L116)).
- **Null & Mock Providers:** Stateless adapters implemented for cost-free, deterministic testing.

### GAP §14 — Modular Improvement & CI Gate (Phase 4)
> *Source: Phase 4 spec §ImprovementEngine*

**Implementation:** [engine.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/improvement_engine/engine.py) + [ci_gate.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/improvement_engine/ci_gate.py)
- **Protected Paths:** `ENGINE_CONFIG`, `IDENTITY_STORE`, etc. enforced via `PATCH_TARGET_PROTECTED(10001)` ([L66](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/improvement_engine/engine.py#L66)).
- **Event Lifecycle:** Implements full proposed → approved → applied/rejected event chain ([L116](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/improvement_engine/engine.py#L116)).
- **Local CI Gate:** Executes `pytest` in a isolated subprocess sandbox.
- **Hot-Swap & Rollback:** Integrated with [ModuleLoader](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/module_loader/loader.py#17-301) for atomic code updates.

